Italy’s Danieli May Invest EU500 Million in Serbia, Beta Says

-- B y   M i s h a   S a v i c
-- 
2011-12-13T07:18:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/italy-s-danieli-may-invest-eu500-million-in-serbia-beta-says.html
Danieli SpA (DAN) ,  Italy ’s biggest maker
of equipment for steel production, is considering a 500 million-
euro ($660 million) investment in production in  Serbia , Beta
 news agency  reported, citing Chairman Gianpietro Benedetti after
meeting with Serbia’s President  Boris Tadic  in northern Italy.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Misha Savic in Belgrade at 
 msavic2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  